  "title": "HAIRSTYLIST",
  "description": "<p><!--td {border: 1px solid #cccccc;}br {mso-data-placement:same-cell;}--></p><p>Provide professional consultation on hair care, scalp conditions, and suitable treatments.</p><p>Recommend suitable products and services based on customers’ needs.</p><p>Assist in treatment procedures such as hair/scalp therapy or product application.</p><p>Educate clients on home care and long-term hair solutions.</p><p>Maintain strong customer relationships and ensure high satisfaction.</p><p>Support the team in achieving monthly sales and service goals.</p><p>Willingness to work night shift and split shift.</p><p>Willingness to work extra hours or weekend if needed.</p>",
